name: Panels Change Each Day
library_note: The color of panels in the cauldron changes each day. Cycles <CLGR>red → blue → green → yellow → white → red<CLNR>.

name: Plachta's Cauldron
library_note: Plachta appears on the right instead of Sophie during Synthesis.

name: Combined Effect
library_note: This cauldron has "Synergy", "Tuning", "Time Limit", and "Color Surroundings" effects.

name: Input Time Limit 20
library_note: Synthesis has a 20 second time limit. Completing Synthesis during this time grants large bonuses.

name: Bonus Display Level 1
library_note: The Synthesis panel display is level 1. Higher display level increases bonus placement at the start of Synthesis.

name: Bonus Display Level 2
library_note: The Synthesis panel display is level 2. Higher display level increases bonus placement at the start of Synthesis.

name: Bonus Display Level 3
library_note: The Synthesis panel display is level 3. Higher display level increases bonus placement at the start of Synthesis.

name: Panel Display Level 3
library_note: The Synthesis panel display is level 3. Higher display level increases Synthesis bonuses on panels.

name: Panel 4x4
library_note: The panel size is 4x4.

name: Panel 5x5
library_note: The panel size is 5x5.

name: Panel 6x6
library_note: The panel size is 6x6.

name: Worn Out Cauldron
library_note: The cauldron Sophie inherited from her grandmother. It was used for a long time, so it only has minimal power left.

name: No Failures
library_note: Performing Synthesis at quality value 0 won't result in failure, and produce the desired item.

name: For Practice
library_note: A practice cauldron for alchemists in training. Since it's for practice, it only has basic functions.

name: Synergy
library_note: Obtaining bonuses that are the same color as the liquid in the cauldron increases effect by 50%.

name: Tuning
library_note: Obtaining bonuses that are the same color as materials already placed causes those materials to gain the same bonus.

name: Time Limit
library_note: 60 second time limit. Exceeding this time will result in <CLGR>failure<CLNR>. Countdown begins after selecting materials and you cannot reselect the cauldron

name: Color Surroundings
library_note: When a material is placed, the Synthesis bonuses in all 8 directions around it become the same color.

name: Quick to Improve
library_note: Increases alchemy experience points by the ratio of the most common synthesis panel color upon item completion.

name: Quality Boost
library_note: Increases item quality by the ratio of the most common synthesis panel color.

name: True Combined Effect
library_note: The ultimate alchemy cauldron, featuring all effects other than "Time Limit".

name: Vertical Flip
library_note: When placing materials, you can press <IM11><IM16> to flip it vertically.

name: Horizontal Flip
library_note: When placing materials, you can press <IM11><IM16> to flip it horizontally.

name: Rotate
library_note: When placing materials, you can press <IM11><IM16> to rotate it.

name: Change Color Red
library_note: Changes the item color to <CLGR>Red<CLNR>.

name: Change Color Blue
library_note: Changes the item color to <CLGR>Blue<CLNR>.

name: Change Color Green
library_note: Changes the item color to <CLGR>Green<CLNR>.

name: Change Color Yellow
library_note: Changes the item color to <CLGR>Yellow<CLNR>.

name: Change Color White
library_note: Changes the item color to <CLGR>White<CLNR>.

name: Add (Ingredient)
library_note: Adds 10 category value to <CLGR>(Ingredient)<CLNR>.

name: Add (Fuel)
library_note: Adds 10 category value to <CLGR>(Fuel)<CLNR>.

name: Add (Medicine Mat)
library_note: Adds 10 category value to <CLGR>(Medicine Mat)<CLNR>.

name: Add (Poison Mat)
library_note: Adds 10 category value to <CLGR>(Poison Mat)<CLNR>.

name: (Ingredient) +5
library_note: Increases <CLGR>(Ingredient)<CLNR> category value by 5.

name: (Powder) +5
library_note: Increases <CLGR>(Gunpowder)<CLNR> category value by 5.

name: (Wood) +5
library_note: Increases <CLGR>(Wood)<CLNR> category value by 5.

name: (Neutralizer) +5
library_note: Increases <CLGR>(Neutralizer)<CLNR> category value by 5.

name: Ultimate Destruction
library_note: Gain ultimate destruction. Increases critical hit damage bonus by 30%.

name: Ultimate Stability
library_note: Gain ultimate stability. Nullifies turn delaying effects by 100%.

name: Ultimate Reversal
library_note: Gain ultimate reversal. 15% of damage taken is converted into MP damage and reduced.

name: Ultimate Mobility
library_note: Gain ultimate mobility. Wait time after using skills is reduced by 20%.

name: Ultimate Regeneration
library_note: Gain ultimate regeneration. Recover 50 HP on every turn.

name: Ultimate Criticality
library_note: Gain ultimate criticality. Increases critical hit rate by 50%.

name: Ultimate Conversion
library_note: Gain ultimate conversion. 20% of damage taken is absorbed into MP.

name: Ultimate Evolution
library_note: Gain ultimate evolution. Greatly enhances stats of the wearer depending on level.

name: Ultimate Vitality
library_note: Gain ultimate vitality. Increases maximum HP by 100.

name: Ultimate Mentality
library_note: Gain ultimate mentality. Increases maximum MP by 100.

name: Ultimate Enhancement
library_note: Gain ultimate enhancement. Increases maximum HP and MP by 50.

name: Ultimate Attack
library_note: Gain ultimate attack power. Increases attack power by 50.

name: Ultimate Defense
library_note: Gain ultimate defense. Increases defense by 50.

name: Ultimate Energy
library_note: Gain ultimate energy. Increases speed by 50.

name: Ultimate Accuracy
library_note: Gain ultimate accuracy. Increases hit rate by 50%.

name: Ultimate Evasion
library_note: Gain ultimate evasion. Increases evasion rate by 15%.

name: Ultimate Fire Resist
library_note: Gain ultimate fire resistance. Gain super fire resistance.

name: Ultimate Ice Resist
library_note: Gain ultimate ice resistance. Gain super ice resistance.

name: Ultimate Thunder Resist
library_note: Gain ultimate lightning resistance. Gain super lightning resistance.

name: Ultimate Resistance
library_note: Gain ultimate resistance. Gain resistance to all status ailments.

name: Ultimate Support
library_note: Gain ultimate support. Enhances Assist action effects by 15%.

name: Ultimate Compensation
library_note: Gain ultimate compensation. Increases skill power by 30%.

name: Ultimate Growth
library_note: Gain ultimate growth. Greatly increases expected damage value.

name: Ultimate Revival
library_note: Gain ultimate revival. Automatically revive on your next turn after being KO'd.

name: Ultimate Turn-Around
library_note: Gain ultimate turn-around. Greatly increases stats when fighting powerful enemies.

name: Ultimate Explosive Force
library_note: Gain ultimate explosive force. Increases damage bonus by 15% during Burst.

name: Ultimate Invulnerability
library_note: Gain ultimate invulnerability. You have a 35% chance to survive with 1 HP when taking damage that would KO you.

name: Ultimate Reduction
library_note: Gain ultimate reduction. You have a 35% chance after a turn to reduce wait time by 25%.

name: Ultimate Mitigation
library_note: Gain ultimate mitigation. Reduces all damage taken by 10%.

name: Ultimate Zeal
library_note: Gain ultimate zeal. Increases Burst Gauge refill rate by 10% when attacking.

name: Ultimate Stunning Force
library_note: Gain ultimate stunning force. Greatly increases Break value when attacking.

name: Ultimate Opposition
library_note: Gain ultimate opposition. Increases damage dealt and reduces damage taken when fighting powerful enemies.
